261
00:22:41.221 --> 00:22:43.431
You not gonna fold 'em?

262
00:22:43.465 --> 00:22:46.399
Albert and I have been in
creases since the day we met.

263
00:22:46.434 --> 00:22:48.781
Our laziness is one of the few
things we have in common.

264
00:22:50.058 --> 00:22:51.646
And the kids of course. Ah...

265
00:22:52.957 --> 00:22:55.615
Albert and I. it's made us.
having them here.

266
00:22:55.650 --> 00:22:57.928
They came to us in
different ways. but...

267
00:22:57.962 --> 00:22:59.861
we love 'em all the same.

268
00:22:59.895 --> 00:23:01.207
So when's this boat arriving?

269
00:23:02.484 --> 00:23:04.417
Before dark.
- What. today?

270
00:23:08.145 --> 00:23:11.562
Albert won't want to set off
for at least another day or two

271
00:23:11.597 --> 00:23:15.670
and if Mal gets his arse in gear
with the food and drink

272
00:23:15.704 --> 00:23:17.810
we'll be able to have
a proper send-off for you.

273
00:23:17.844 --> 00:23:19.605
Can't I just stay?

274
00:23:19.639 --> 00:23:21.400
Can't you just take me in?
Like the others.

275
00:23:21.745 --> 00:23:23.022
Ah. love.

276
00:23:23.056 --> 00:23:25.127
Look. I can work.
I'll do whatever you want.

277
00:23:25.783 --> 00:23:26.784
I know you would.

278
00:23:28.165 --> 00:23:30.063
But you killed someone. Darren.

279
00:23:30.098 --> 00:23:34.413
Staying here longer than needed.
it's not safe for you. nor us.

280
00:23:47.322 --> 00:23:49.635
[HE GASPS]

281
00:24:04.235 --> 00:24:06.962
[HE STIFLES A YELL]

282
00:24:21.011 --> 00:24:22.150
[STAPLER CLICKS]

283
00:24:22.702 --> 00:24:24.497
[HE GROANS]

284
00:24:26.119 --> 00:24:27.466
[STAPLER CLICKS]

285
00:24:29.916 --> 00:24:31.746
[DISTANT CHATTER]

286
00:24:40.133 --> 00:24:41.238
[FRANK]
Are you lost?

287
00:24:42.619 --> 00:24:43.930
Toilet?

288
00:24:43.965 --> 00:24:45.863
[FRANK] Right next to you.
Where it says toilet.

289
00:24:45.898 --> 00:24:48.176
Piss only.
Shitter's out of order.

290
00:24:50.316 --> 00:24:52.076
Lucky me.
- [FRANK] Lucky for both of us.

291
00:27:02.724 --> 00:27:03.483
[DOOR OPENS]

292
00:27:03.518 --> 00:27:05.900
[DISTANT CHATTER]

293
00:27:09.420 --> 00:27:11.802
[HAND DRYER WHIRS]

294
00:27:40.969 --> 00:27:41.901
[CAR DOOR SHUTS]

295
00:28:12.414 --> 00:28:13.692
[IN DANISH]

296
00:28:37.957 --> 00:28:38.820
What can I get you?

297
00:28:43.618 --> 00:28:44.481
No. no. no--

298
00:28:44.515 --> 00:28:45.724
[GUNSHOT]
- [FRANK GRUNTS]

299
00:29:08.539 --> 00:29:10.576
[INDISTINCT CHATTER IN DANISH]

300
00:31:18.255 --> 00:31:20.223
[GIRL] Oi. come on!
- Alright?

301
00:31:20.257 --> 00:31:21.155
[GIRL]
Yeah. alright.

302
00:31:21.189 --> 00:31:21.845
Who're you?

303
00:31:22.777 --> 00:31:24.675
No one.
- New recruit. Mum?

304
00:31:24.710 --> 00:31:27.161
Nah. Just passin' through.
Be gone by morning.

305
00:31:27.195 --> 00:31:28.334
Oi. what's all this?

306
00:31:28.369 --> 00:31:30.440
Are you fucking kidding me
or what?

307
00:31:30.474 --> 00:31:32.407
Oi! You stop walkin'. old man!

308
00:31:32.442 --> 00:31:33.443
Evie...
- No talking!

309
00:31:34.202 --> 00:31:35.548
I'm telling you now. son

310
00:31:35.583 --> 00:31:38.448
if he drops my shopping.
there'll be bloody hell to pay.

311
00:31:38.482 --> 00:31:41.278
He's with the boy.
Go on. Give him a hand.

312
00:31:41.313 --> 00:31:42.970
No. you fucking don't.

313
00:31:43.004 --> 00:31:44.730
You just drove right past me
with these bags.

314
00:31:44.764 --> 00:31:47.181
I could just about throw these
in that house from here.

315
00:31:47.215 --> 00:31:48.699
Where were you when
I fucking needed you

316
00:31:48.734 --> 00:31:50.287
halfway to breaking
my fucking neck. huh?

317
00:31:50.322 --> 00:31:51.185
Are you his dad?

318
00:31:52.807 --> 00:31:54.982
Darren! Get back inside!

319
00:31:56.811 --> 00:31:58.744
Oi. There's a lot
of stock left over.

320
00:31:58.778 --> 00:32:00.159
You been gone over a week.

321
00:32:00.194 --> 00:32:01.540
I expect you to shift the lot.

322
00:32:01.574 --> 00:32:03.956
Nah. we couldn't deliver
'owt to Mikey Cartwright.

323
00:32:03.991 --> 00:32:05.993
Not gonna be able to
anytime soon either.

324
00:32:06.027 --> 00:32:07.684
Someone torched him
in his kiosk.

325
00:32:07.718 --> 00:32:09.548
Torched him?
- [GIRL] Aye.

326
00:32:09.582 --> 00:32:11.412
He went up with all his stock.

327
00:32:11.446 --> 00:32:13.069
Police had cordoned
it off before we got there.

328
00:32:14.484 --> 00:32:16.382
You!
- [MAL] Evie!

329
00:32:16.417 --> 00:32:17.694
[EVIE] I knew there was
something wrong!

330
00:32:17.728 --> 00:32:20.110
[MAL] Evie!
- Gimme the gun!

331
00:32:20.145 --> 00:32:21.698
Gimme the fucking gun!

332
00:32:25.115 --> 00:32:27.152
That's Mikey's metal.

333
00:32:27.186 --> 00:32:28.981
And this. this is my slug.

334
00:32:31.777 --> 00:32:32.743
Tell me the truth!

335
00:32:33.641 --> 00:32:35.332
Who the fuck did you kill?

336
00:32:35.367 --> 00:32:37.714
[MAL] Evie!
- Look at me. look at me!

337
00:32:37.748 --> 00:32:39.750
Evie... Evie!
- [EVIE] Tell me!

338
00:32:39.785 --> 00:32:41.338
Who the fuck did you kill?
- Just...

339
00:32:41.373 --> 00:32:42.132
Finn Wallace!

340
00:32:48.656 --> 00:32:49.553
Finn?

341
00:32:50.071 --> 00:32:50.969
Yeah.

342
00:32:53.350 --> 00:32:55.249
Finn? No!
- [MAL] I couldn't in all right

343
00:32:55.283 --> 00:32:57.078
tell you. could I?
- [EVIE] No! No!

344
00:32:57.113 --> 00:33:00.461
Cos you knew. you knew
that I'd never fucking hide him.

345
00:33:00.495 --> 00:33:02.704
Get away from the window!
- [EVIE] Why?

346
00:33:02.739 --> 00:33:05.604
Why? Just tell me one thing.

347
00:33:05.638 --> 00:33:07.571
Why would you go after him?
- We didn't.

348
00:33:07.606 --> 00:33:09.470
He didn't know who he was...

349
00:33:09.504 --> 00:33:12.059
Darren. will you step away
from the fucking window!

350
00:33:14.199 --> 00:33:14.785
Dad...

351
00:33:36.635 --> 00:33:39.017
[GUNFIRE]

352
00:34:01.246 --> 00:34:03.351
[GUNSHOTS]

353
00:34:03.386 --> 00:34:05.526
[GUNFIRE]
- Oh. fuck!

354
00:34:09.288 --> 00:34:10.634
[EVIE SCREAMS]

355
00:34:18.435 --> 00:34:20.334
[SHE SCREAMS]

356
00:34:23.544 --> 00:34:25.649
[DOOR CREAKS]

357
00:34:25.684 --> 00:34:27.479
[GUNFIRE RESUMES]
- [HE YELLS]

358
00:34:31.897 --> 00:34:32.898
Come on!

359
00:34:55.265 --> 00:34:56.335
Get Darren!

360
00:35:12.386 --> 00:35:14.457
[HE WAILS]

361
00:35:16.355 --> 00:35:17.460
[SHE GRUNTS]

362
00:35:19.013 --> 00:35:20.877
Mum. please...

363
00:35:26.193 --> 00:35:28.850
Liam! Don't let them
surround the house!

364
00:35:38.895 --> 00:35:41.449
[HE YELLS]

365
00:35:41.484 --> 00:35:43.382
[GUNFIRE STOPS]

366
00:35:56.015 --> 00:35:57.155
[GUNSHOT]

367
00:36:04.023 --> 00:36:06.302
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

368
00:36:10.340 --> 00:36:11.721
[GUNFIRE STOPS]

369
00:36:18.590 --> 00:36:19.591
[IN DANISH]

370
00:36:45.444 --> 00:36:47.239
[GUNFIRE]

371
00:36:53.763 --> 00:36:54.729
Come!

372
00:36:55.592 --> 00:36:57.767
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

373
00:37:16.441 --> 00:37:17.476
Evie!

374
00:37:21.929 --> 00:37:25.726
[SOUND MUTES]
- [SHE BREATHES SLOWLY]

375
00:37:52.960 --> 00:37:55.411
[LOUD DISTORTION]
- [MUFFLED YELL]

376
00:37:55.445 --> 00:37:56.619
[SHE SCREAMS]

377
00:38:00.692 --> 00:38:01.934
[EVIE SCREAMS]

378
00:38:03.557 --> 00:38:04.592
[GUNFIRE OVERHEAD]

379
00:38:04.627 --> 00:38:06.353
[MAN SCREAMS]

380
00:38:15.431 --> 00:38:16.811
[MAN SCREAMS]

381
00:38:18.054 --> 00:38:20.367
Jesus! The roof!

382
00:38:21.782 --> 00:38:23.784
Now! Get on the roof!

383
00:38:25.061 --> 00:38:27.063
You see anybody's feet
other than ours

384
00:38:27.097 --> 00:38:28.582
you fucking shoot them.
you hear me?

385
00:38:33.103 --> 00:38:34.312
Darren!

386
00:38:35.105 --> 00:38:36.072
Darren!

387
00:38:46.565 --> 00:38:47.877
[DARREN YELLS]

388
00:38:53.779 --> 00:38:55.091
[KINNEY MUTTERS]

389
00:40:38.643 --> 00:40:40.576
[FOOTSTEPS OVERHEAD]

390
00:40:49.757 --> 00:40:51.725
[GUNFIRE]

391
00:40:54.590 --> 00:40:56.281
[DEVICE BEEPS]
- [EXPLOSION]

392
00:41:00.803 --> 00:41:01.873
[EXPLOSION]

393
00:41:08.155 --> 00:41:10.088
[GUNFIRE]

394
00:41:14.299 --> 00:41:15.680
[MAN]
Go. go. go!

395
00:41:18.993 --> 00:41:20.685
[GUNFIRE]

396
00:41:28.106 --> 00:41:29.279
[HE GRUNTS]
- [GUNFIRE]

397
00:41:36.010 --> 00:41:38.150
[DISTANT GUNFIRE]

398
00:41:41.982 --> 00:41:42.948
[IN DANISH]

399
00:41:58.964 --> 00:42:00.863
[DISTANT GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

400
00:42:24.714 --> 00:42:25.957
[HE YELLS]

401
00:42:36.657 --> 00:42:37.555
Cover me!

402
00:42:40.143 --> 00:42:41.386
[HE ROARS]
- [GUNFIRE]

403
00:42:51.154 --> 00:42:52.362
[MAL YELLS]

404
00:42:56.815 --> 00:42:59.162
[MAL YELLS]

405
00:43:05.410 --> 00:43:07.308
[GUNFIRE]

406
00:43:10.070 --> 00:43:11.278
[HE GASPS]

407
00:43:34.681 --> 00:43:37.338
[GUNFIRE]

408
00:44:35.880 --> 00:44:38.676
[SOUND MUTES]

409
00:44:58.040 --> 00:44:59.800
[EXPLOSION]

410
00:45:20.959 --> 00:45:24.411
[EARS RING]

411
00:45:51.472 --> 00:45:54.924
[SHE BREATHES HEAVILY]

412
00:46:01.241 --> 00:46:03.139
[KINNEY GROANS]

413
00:46:08.075 --> 00:46:09.525
[HE COUGHS]

414
00:46:15.324 --> 00:46:16.601
[KINNEY COUGHS]
- Come on.

415
00:46:19.673 --> 00:46:21.640
[DARREN]
Get your fucking hands off me.

416
00:46:21.675 --> 00:46:23.539
You fucking killed him...
You fucking killed Ioan!

417
00:46:24.126 --> 00:46:25.610
You're fucking evil!

418
00:46:25.644 --> 00:46:28.164
Get off me! Get off me!

419
00:46:38.554 --> 00:46:40.936
I'll hold 'em back.
long as I can.

420
00:46:40.970 --> 00:46:41.557
Thank you.

421
00:46:42.282 --> 00:46:43.939
No. no. Evie. please.

422
00:46:43.973 --> 00:46:45.630
Come with us.
Evie. please! No!

423
00:46:47.252 --> 00:46:48.944
Be worth it. boy.

424
00:46:48.978 --> 00:46:50.324
No. no. please. come with us!

425
00:46:50.359 --> 00:46:52.257
Please. Evie! No! Get off!

426
00:46:52.292 --> 00:46:54.052
Please. Evie come with us!

427
00:46:54.087 --> 00:46:57.124
No. Evie! No! Evie!

428
00:47:13.140 --> 00:47:14.038
Where does it lead?

429
00:47:17.144 --> 00:47:19.526
[GUNFIRE]
- [SHE YELLS]

430
00:47:41.651 --> 00:47:42.860
Give me the gun.

431
00:47:44.516 --> 00:47:46.001
Give it to me!
Hey! That's mine.

432
00:48:01.257 --> 00:48:02.327
Here.

433
00:48:03.570 --> 00:48:04.605
It's worth something now.

434
00:48:05.537 --> 00:48:08.437
[DISTANT BELL RINGS]

435
00:48:08.471 --> 00:48:09.645
That'll be Al.

436
00:48:11.060 --> 00:48:12.199
Come on.

437
00:48:13.338 --> 00:48:14.719
We can still make it.

438
00:48:46.475 --> 00:48:48.615
For a week. I've had
one bullet left in this gun.

439
00:48:50.513 --> 00:48:52.722
And every day I saw it.
I swore I'd use it on you.

440
00:48:56.036 --> 00:48:57.693
Take more than that
to put me down.

441
00:49:01.179 --> 00:49:02.180
I've done it before.

442
00:49:04.044 --> 00:49:05.356
It only took a second.

443
00:49:06.253 --> 00:49:07.220
No. son.

444
00:49:09.429 --> 00:49:10.568
It took a lot more.

445
00:49:14.330 --> 00:49:15.504
Come on.

446
00:49:15.538 --> 00:49:17.264
[DARREN SOBS]
- Come on...

447
00:49:18.852 --> 00:49:20.612
You let me get you
on that boat. son

448
00:49:21.751 --> 00:49:23.512
and I'll let you pull
the fucking trigger.

449
00:49:23.546 --> 00:49:24.720
[DARREN GRUNTS]
- Come on.

450
00:49:26.204 --> 00:49:28.034
[DARREN SOBS]
- Come on.

451
00:49:28.448 --> 00:49:29.621
Come on.

452
00:49:33.522 --> 00:49:35.006
[DARREN SOBS]
- Come on!

453
00:49:37.767 --> 00:49:39.700
[KINNEY GROWLS]
- [DARREN GRUNTS]

454
00:49:44.567 --> 00:49:47.329
[BOAT ENGINE RUMBLES]

455
00:49:47.812 --> 00:49:50.159
[THEY GRUNT]

456
00:49:56.648 --> 00:49:58.409
[ALBERT]
No. no. no. no. Evie...

457
00:49:58.443 --> 00:50:01.136
You keep that running!
We had a fucking deal!

458
00:50:01.170 --> 00:50:03.655
Kinney! Where the fuck
is my wife?

459
00:50:03.690 --> 00:50:05.209
[GUNFIRE]

460
00:50:09.730 --> 00:50:10.697
[DARREN GRUNTS]

461
00:50:14.908 --> 00:50:16.737
[GUNFIRE]

462
00:50:26.851 --> 00:50:28.439
[KINNEY ROARS]

463
00:50:29.267 --> 00:50:31.304
[GUNSHOTS]

464
00:50:31.338 --> 00:50:32.512
[GUN CLICKS]

465
00:50:34.790 --> 00:50:36.378
[KINNEY ROARS]

466
00:50:39.243 --> 00:50:41.762
[SOUND MUTES]

467
00:50:58.400 --> 00:51:00.678
[DARREN SOBS]

468
00:51:02.128 --> 00:51:03.853
[DARREN GROANS]

469
00:51:09.652 --> 00:51:10.722
You get on that boat!

470
00:51:11.861 --> 00:51:13.346
You head straight.
- Dad. please.

471
00:51:13.829 --> 00:51:15.520
[DARREN GROANS]

472
00:51:15.934 --> 00:51:16.832
Shh...

473
00:51:24.460 --> 00:51:25.841
You push it as hard as you can.

474
00:51:28.499 --> 00:51:29.810
As far as she'll go.

475
00:51:30.432 --> 00:51:32.123
[DARREN WHIMPERS]

476
00:51:32.158 --> 00:51:33.124
Come on. boy.

477
00:51:34.953 --> 00:51:35.920
Stay strong.

478
00:51:41.822 --> 00:51:42.789
Dad...

479
00:51:43.686 --> 00:51:44.722
Son.

480
00:51:46.689 --> 00:51:47.897
[GUNSHOT]

481
00:52:22.449 --> 00:52:23.588
Why'd you pick him?

482
00:52:30.940 --> 00:52:31.803
[GUNSHOT]

483
00:52:52.859 --> 00:52:54.412
[GUNSHOT ECHOES]

484
00:53:02.627 --> 00:53:03.939
[PHONE DIALS]

485
00:53:05.423 --> 00:53:06.873
[WOMAN]
Hello. Mr Kapadia's office.

486
00:53:07.701 --> 00:53:09.807
Hello. 246.

487
00:53:09.841 --> 00:53:11.222
[WOMAN]
Yes. sir. Immediately.

488
00:53:16.331 --> 00:53:17.401
[LEIF]
We're done here.

489
00:53:17.953 --> 00:53:18.954
[JEVAN]
Everyone?

490
00:53:20.542 --> 00:53:21.750
More.

491
00:53:21.784 --> 00:53:23.234
[JEVAN] Remove all trace
and return to London.

492
00:53:23.855 --> 00:53:24.891
Orders just came in.

493
00:53:26.375 --> 00:53:27.514
We've got a new target.

494
00:53:28.653 --> 00:53:29.758
Another son.
